Mwaramutse neza?

Mfashe uyu mwanya nshimira abarimu ba GS MBUYE twasangiraga ku meza amwe, twasimburanaga muri Class twuzuza inshingano, twajyaga inama twungurana ibitekerezo biganisha mu kunoza akazi, abarimu bansuye mu gihe narindwaye binyuze muri gahunda ya Solidarity, Soridality nirambe muri GS MBUYE. 

Ndashimira ubuyobozi bwa GS MBUYE bwanyakiriye bukandindira umutekano mu kazi kugeza uyu munsi.

Ndashimira ubuyobozi bw'akarere ka Ngoma ku mikoranire twagiranye mu kunoza ishyirwa mu bikorwa ry'amategeko agenga imicungire y'abakozi ba Leta harimo n'abarimu. 

Nta gushidikanya, experiences nkuye kuri GS MBUYE ni Kimwe mu by'ingenzi bigize C.V yanjye. 

Barimu banyakubahwa muri hano, ku bwanjye mbona narakoze uko nshoboye kugirango nuzuze inshingano zanjye nka mwarimu ziteganywa mu ngingo ya .. y'iteka rya Minisitiri rishyiraho sitati igenga abakozi bo mu mashuri, bityo rero kugirango iyo ntego igerweho hari aho bitagenze neza. 

Ku bw'iyo mpamvu nagaragaje mu gika cya 8 cy'iyi message,  nsabye imbabazi uwo ariwe wese (If any)naba narabwiye nabi, naba naratesheje agaciro mu ruhame, naba narambuye icyubahiro cye, umudendezo we n'uburenganzira ntayegayezwa, naba ntaratabaye ari mu kaga kandi mbifitiye ubushobozi; yaba umwarimu, umuyobozi w'ikigo,  cyangwa umunyeshuri. Nsabye imbabazi muri rusange ku bitaragenze neza kuko nanjye ndi umuntu si ndi umumalayika, nanjye nakosa, nanjye ngira amarangamutima anyemerera gusubiza (reactions) ku kibaye mu buryo butandukanye n'ubwundi, ariko nanjye nagirwa inama nkumva cyangwa nahanwa nkikosora. Muri rusange nta mutima mubi. 


Ndabamenyesha ko nta kiri umukozi ku kigo cya GS MBUYE.

Nasoza ngira nti: "Agafuni kabagara ubucuti ni akarenge".
 Ndabashimiye, mugire amahoro y'Imana.